            .tile.is-child
              p.title Know more than your competitors
              p In just two days, you will learn much more than your competitors, who attend narrow-focused conferences. We focus on the core areas that are paramount to your success ‚Äî software architecture, clean code and leadership. All noise is removed. Start preparing for the role of software architect, engineering leader or CTO today. 
            .tile.is-child
              p.title Earn certificate of attendance 
                i.has-text-warning.fas.fa-trophy(aria-hidden="true")
              p After the conference, we issue an official, nice, laminated certificate of accomplishment, confirming the attendance of the conference. Use it for for boosting your credibility, enrich your LinkedIn profile or build a nice certificate wall.
            .tile.is-child
              p.title Get salary raise
              p We talk to our permanent attendees and many report increase in salary. Depending on the market, architects earn 25-70% than developers. Want to turn your 3K into 5K? Jump on the bus and learn things that matter.
            .tile.is-child
              p.title Enjoy perfect coffee by 
                img.is-inline.image.is-64x64.is-rounded(src="/images/illy.png")
              p What's the best coffee on the planet? It's Illy. Illy coffees are blended from arabica beans from multiple sources. The grounds are packaged in steel canisters and pressurized with an inert gas rather than air. DevTernity runs on Illy. And, like all best things in life, it's free.
            .tile.is-child
              p.title We buy you a lunch
              p You have only one stomack, but many conferences try to kill you with a baguette made of stone. We serve tasty, freshly cooked, organic food. Meat eater? Vegetarian? Vegan? We won't leave you hungry.
            .tile.is-child
              p.title Learn directly from industry influencers
              p Tired of Captain Obvious, marketing and Agile bullshit? We, too. We only invite speakers with outstanding technical and public speaking skills. Any exceptions, such as sponsored talks? Sorry, not at this conference.
            .tile.is-child
              p.title Have unbiased views
              p Do you know what's the real purpose of any vendor, technology or a language specific conference? Think of Kubernetes, Docker, Amazon... It's to make you dependent on the vendor for products and services, so you can't use another vendor without substantial switching costs. It's called "vendor lock-in". Here at DevTernity, you will get unbiased view on technology, trends and solutions. No sales. No hidden messages. Ever.
            .tile.is-child
              p.title Join respectful community
              p We are committed to providing a welcoming and harassment-free environment for participants of all races, gender and trans statuses, sexual orientations, physical abilities, physical appearances, and beliefs. 
                a(href="https://devternity.com/code_of_conduct.html") Here
                |  is our public commitment to doing all we can to ensure your safety.
            .tile.is-child
              p.title Use internet like a boss
